---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Accordion, AccordionItem, } from 'accessible-astro-components'
---
<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Uppercut" 
  description="We take your privacy seriously. Read our privacy policy to learn more about how we use your data."
  image="https://www.tryuppercut.com/og-image.png"
  url="https://www.tryuppercut.com"
>
<main>
    <!--Hero-->
    <div class="overlay"></div>
    <section class="p-t-14 dark-bg-black">
      <div class="container container-xl">
        <!--headline & text-->
        <div class="section-title all-center">
          <h2 class="h2 m-b-6 md-w-75">
            Privacy Policy
          </h2>
            <p class="gray-500 text-xl md-w-50">
                Our commitment to your privacy
            </p>
            <p class="m-t-8 m-x-14 text-center font-size-lg font-semibold mb-8">At Distilled, we are committed to protecting the privacy and security of our customers' personal information. This Privacy Policy explains our data protection practices, including how we collect, use, and disclose personal information, as well as the rights and choices available to our customers regarding their personal information.</p>
            <h3 class="h3 m-b-6 m-t-8 md-w-75">
                What we collect
            </h3>
            <p class="m-x-14 align-left font-size-xl mb-8">We collect personal information from our customers in a variety of ways, including when they register for an account, purchase products or services, use our website, or communicate with us. The personal information we collect may include, but is not limited to, name, email address, phone number, and payment information.
            </p>
            <h3 class="h3 m-b-6 m-t-8 md-w-75">
                How we use your information
            </h3>
            <p class="m-x-14 align-left font-size-xl mb-8">We use personal information for a variety of purposes, including to provide products and services, process transactions, respond to customer inquiries, and to improve our website and services. We may also use personal information to send promotional communications, such as newsletters, special offers, and surveys. We may also use personal information to provide you with information about our products and services, or to provide you with information about third-party products and services that we believe may be of interest to you. 
            </p>
            <h3 class="h3 m-b-6 m-t-8 md-w-75">
                How we share your information 
            </h3>
            <p class="m-x-14 align-left font-size-xl mb-8">We do not sell or rent personal information to third parties for their marketing purposes. However, we may share personal information with third-party service providers who perform services on our behalf, such as processing payments, providing customer service, and conducting marketing and research. These third-party service providers are required to maintain the confidentiality and security of personal information and are not permitted to use it for any purpose other than providing services on our behalf. We may also disclose personal information in response to legal requirements, such as a subpoena or court order, or to protect the safety and security of our customers and the public. 
            </p>
            <h3 class="h3 m-b-6 m-t-8 md-w-75">
                Your data protection rights
            </h3>
            <p class="m-x-14 align-left font-size-xl mb-8">You have the right to request access to, rectification or erasure of, or restriction of processing of, your personal information. You also have the right to object to processing of your personal information and the right to receive your personal information in a portable format. Additionally, you have the right to withdraw your consent to our processing of your personal information at any time. You can exercise these rights by contacting us via email.
            </p>
            <h3 class="h3 m-b-6 m-t-8 md-w-75">
                Changes to this Privacy Policy
            </h3>
            <p class="m-x-14 align-left font-size-xl mb-8">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes to our data protection practices. If we make any material changes to this Privacy Policy, we will notify you by posting the updated Privacy Policy on our website and, where appropriate, through other means such as email. 
            </p>
            <h3 class="h3 m-b-6 m-t-8 md-w-75">
                Contact
            </h3>
            <p class="m-x-14 align-left font-size-xl mb-8"> If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our data protection practices, please contact us at hello@tryuppercut. 
            </p>




